summary:
I'm doing a digital transformation project in education and finance, leading a research center for new education formats, and teaching ML project management at St. Petersburg State University.

Key projects:
- Immersive course with interactive VR simulation training in sales skills for the front line - more than 1000 employees trained.
- Chatbot for the VTB application "My investments" (https://rb.ru/longread/investments/) - more than 3,000 calls per day through the chatbot;
- VR-mortgage platform (https://www.banki.ru/news/lenta/?id=10912141) - the first deals in Russia for the sale of apartments in the metaverse;
- VR investments (https://broker.vtb.ru/servnews/art_detail/1112540/) - sold products in 10 cities through VR helmets;
- Development of a system with contactless and biometric authentication;
- Development of an IoT platform for smart housing and communal services (collection of meter data and automatic unloading of payments in exchange for commission income and an increase in advertising campaigns);
- Micro-modular training application for the staff of the contact center of products;
- Platform Open API Association;
- Official qualification of VTB in Yandex.Alisa;
- Platform for virtual assistants;
- Geoanalytics for marketing and office management, etc.


- Managed project for improving labor productivity and reducing cost in 240 branches in cooperation with  McKinsey&Company 
- Implemented new POS positions: meter-greeter and client manager
- Implemented virtual queuing in regional branches
- Development of a brach-rate sales system 
- Development of bank quality management system, fully implemented by the main board
- Analysis of bank products. Analysis and modeling of business processes
- Creation and implementation of a customer service appraisal system for 450 branches
- Creation and reconciliation of the bank’s corporate regulatory documents and orders
- Budget-holder. Cost planning and control. Actual vs. plan comparisons
- Setting of KPI for regional branch executives. Training methodologies
- Organisation of insurance company UralSib presentations for customers and partners
- Expert articles in professional magazines. Participation in symposiums and seminars
- Creation of reports and papers for the main board
- Software design of mortgage insurance calculator
- Design of group healthcare insurance product for children
- Market research and analysis. Oversaw customer satisfaction and quality measurement project. Project administration
- Collaboration with other Head Office departments and regional branches
